=Six Sisters=

14
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:38,140
=Episode 20=

15
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:52,630
That's a lot of thunder

16
00:01:53,510 --> 00:01:54,760
for this time of year.

17
00:01:56,150 --> 00:01:56,990
It's unusual.

18
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,120
Yes, it is.

19
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,560
I hope nothing happens.

20
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,200
The weather's really bad.

21
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:39,350
Watch out, guys. Here's the roof.

22
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,120
We're watching.

23
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,000
Make sure it's aligned.

24
00:02:44,670 --> 00:02:45,510
Ok.

25
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:52,560
Jianguo,

26
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,560
catch this.

27
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:54,760
Give me.

28
00:02:55,130 --> 00:02:56,000
Be careful with your hands.

29
00:02:58,070 --> 00:02:58,910
Come.

30
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,510
The bottom should be aligned.

31
00:03:00,510 --> 00:03:01,400
I'll push it from the outside.

32
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:05,440
Is it ok?

33
00:03:08,550 --> 00:03:09,390
Uncle Hongyu

34
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:10,700
is working so hard.

35
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:11,580
Of course.

36
00:03:11,580 --> 00:03:13,160
(He Xiangdong)

37
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,440
What are you doing?

38
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:15,280
Get to work.

39
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,390
- Come on.
- Lazy guy.

40
00:03:18,350 --> 00:03:19,760
Take a break. Have some water.

41
00:03:20,350 --> 00:03:21,200
- Come on.
- Mom.

42
00:03:21,550 --> 00:03:22,390
Take this.

43
00:03:22,510 --> 00:03:23,370
Be careful.

44
00:03:23,390 --> 00:03:24,790
- Mom.
- Take a break.

45
00:03:26,230 --> 00:03:27,550
Let's take turns

46
00:03:27,830 --> 00:03:30,040
and try to build it in one go, ok?

47
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:30,880
- Ok.
- Ok.

48
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,480
Hongyu, have some water.

49
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:35,200
Fang Tao, would you like some water?

50
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:37,550
I'll get it.

51
00:03:37,550 --> 00:03:38,800
- I'll drink when I'm done.
- Ok.

52
00:03:51,950 --> 00:03:52,790
Mom.

53
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,280
- Mom.
- Mom.

54
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,160
Mom.

55
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:00,510
Mom. Go inside and check.

56
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,600
Ok.

57
00:04:07,550 --> 00:04:09,950
Walk around and feel it.

58
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:14,390
With Mom's dexterous hands,

59
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,990
our family will be prosperous again.

60
00:04:17,190 --> 00:04:18,920
That's true.

61
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,400
Now we have so many family members.

62
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,520
It's so lively.

63
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,520
Mom, what do you think?

64
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:26,990
You know, I really feel different.

65
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:30,230
I feel like I'm in the palace of heaven.

66
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,520
Good. Thank you, guys.

67
00:04:35,790 --> 00:04:37,350
Mom is happy with our work.

68
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,960
Mom, when you give the order,

69
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:41,190
we will be

70
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,160
at your beck and call.

71
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,000
- Ok.
- Yeah.

72
00:04:43,020 --> 00:04:44,190
- We are on your call.
- Thanks.

73
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:46,480
Thanks, guys.

74
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:49,230
Can we fit all these members

75
00:04:49,230 --> 00:04:50,640
in the house?

76
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:52,750
One table for adults, one table for kids.

77
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:54,600
- Yeah.
- Let's celebrate today.

78
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,640
Get inside and eat.

79
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:56,750
- Ok.
- Let's eat.

80
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:58,550
Let's eat.

81
00:04:59,550 --> 00:05:00,520
- Come on.
- Have a few drinks.

82
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,800
Let's eat.

83
00:05:09,350 --> 00:05:10,190
- Jiali.
- Ok.

84
00:05:10,550 --> 00:05:12,840
Bring your dad's cup over here.

85
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:13,680
Okay.

86
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:17,920
Your dad misses you all in heaven.

87
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:18,800
Today,

88
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,020
we have sons, daughters,

89
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:22,750
husbands, and wives here.

90
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,160
It's a joyous and harmonious day.

91
00:05:25,430 --> 00:05:28,230
Finally, our family is complete again.

92
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,350
Since we're a family,

93
00:05:30,350 --> 00:05:32,350
we should act like a family.

94
00:05:32,550 --> 00:05:34,160
From now on, let's be united

95
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:35,550
and look out for each other.

96
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:38,160
Don't let me do all the talking.

97
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,120
You should say something too.

98
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:41,280
You're good at talking.

99
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,310
Home, home.

100
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:54,520
What's home?

101
00:05:59,350 --> 00:06:00,600
What's home?

102
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,430
You tell us.

103
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,000
Hongyu.

104
00:06:04,230 --> 00:06:05,070
You tell us.

105
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,880
Home?

106
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:10,480
Go ahead.

107
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,360
Say it.

108
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:15,350
Home is not a restaurant.

109
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,040
Home is not a hotel.

110
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,600
Home is not a place for business.

111
00:06:22,790 --> 00:06:24,720
Where there's Mom, there's home.

112
00:06:27,790 --> 00:06:29,790
Where there's my wife, there's home.

113
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:37,550
Jiawen, you guys should say something too.

114
00:06:38,310 --> 00:06:39,150
You say it.

115
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:43,160
Home should be tidy and clean.

116
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:45,640
- Yeah.
- Jiali, say something.

117
00:06:47,190 --> 00:06:48,030
Home...

118
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,160
Home is

119
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,440
peace of mind.

120
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,040
Home is solidity.

121
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:59,350
Home is unity.

122
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:01,110
Well side.

123
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:05,640
Your dad wanted his family to prosper.

124
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:08,640
I'll drink this on behalf of him,

125
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,560
ok?

126
00:07:10,430 --> 00:07:11,520
- Come on.
- Come.

127
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:16,680
Are you ok?

128
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:20,270
Jiali,

129
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:22,750
when I'm gone,

130
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:26,040
unite with your sisters and brothers-in-law

131
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:28,350
to take good care of mom.

132
00:07:29,990 --> 00:07:32,550
Mom, it's the Spring Festival.

133
00:07:32,550 --> 00:07:33,960
Don't say anything inauspicious.

134
00:07:34,350 --> 00:07:35,920
Ok, you're right.

135
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:37,550
Let's eat. No more talking.

136
00:07:37,870 --> 00:07:39,110
- Eat.
- Eat.

137
00:07:41,630 --> 00:07:43,430
♪Those who are watching are crying♪

138
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:47,790
May you all be like the carp

139
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,550
leaping over the Dragon Gate.

140
00:07:49,550 --> 00:07:50,390
Great!

141
00:07:50,790 --> 00:07:51,790
Thanks, Grandma.

142
00:07:51,790 --> 00:07:52,750
Wish you good health!

143
00:07:52,790 --> 00:07:53,630
Good health!

144
00:07:56,410 --> 00:08:00,060
♪Over a bed and a candy♪

145
00:08:00,430 --> 00:08:02,280
♪By the time we learn to share♪

146
00:08:02,570 --> 00:08:06,330
♪We are far apart♪

147
00:08:07,590 --> 00:08:10,990
♪The geese♪

148
00:08:11,310 --> 00:08:14,200
♪The stars♪

149
00:08:15,110 --> 00:08:21,830
♪Will come back to where they started♪

150
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:25,370
♪Don't be afraid♪

151
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:30,000
♪Wandering like a willow floss♪

152
00:08:30,550 --> 00:08:37,310
♪There's always a light at home♪

153
00:08:38,190 --> 00:08:40,160
Jiali, have some water.

154
00:08:40,670 --> 00:08:43,120
Four jin. I'll get you more when you're done.

155
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,190
Take this.

156
00:08:46,470 --> 00:08:48,000
What for? I don't need your money.

157
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,240
You're not well-off, either.

158
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:51,160
You don't take my money every time.

159
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:54,280
I don't feel good about it.

160
00:08:55,070 --> 00:08:56,830
Still, I'm better off than you.

161
00:08:58,070 --> 00:08:59,670
Has the factory started to transfer you guys?

162
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:01,160
Yes.

163
00:09:01,310 --> 00:09:02,240
But the point is that,

164
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,070
there aren't many jobs.

165
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:06,830
I'll let Jianguo ask around

166
00:09:06,830 --> 00:09:08,160
and see if there are any opportunities.

167
00:09:08,710 --> 00:09:10,040
There is one.

168
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:12,070
There's a big pharmaceutical plant

169
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,830
going up nearby.

170
00:09:13,830 --> 00:09:14,880
They're hiring now.

171
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:17,070
Weiguo is pulling strings

172
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,430
to get me a job in there.

173
00:09:18,670 --> 00:09:19,510
That's good.

174
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:21,280
Yeah, he went to his elder brother.

175
00:09:21,710 --> 00:09:23,240
He has a student

176
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,430
who works at the personnel bureau

177
00:09:24,430 --> 00:09:26,280
or in the development zone.

178
00:09:26,470 --> 00:09:27,470
He might be able to help.

179
00:09:28,670 --> 00:09:29,510
But...

180
00:09:30,730 --> 00:09:32,280
But he hasn't got back to us yet.

181
00:09:33,430 --> 00:09:35,280
His brother and sister-in-law

182
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:38,120
are very stingy and petty.

183
00:09:39,470 --> 00:09:42,160
Still, they may do Weiguo the favor.

184
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:43,240
That's true.

185
00:09:43,590 --> 00:09:44,430
Come.

186
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,080
Weiguo.

187
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,280
- Jiali, you're here.
- Aunt.

188
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:48,390
Guangming.

189
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:50,430
You rarely visit us.

190
00:09:50,430 --> 00:09:51,430
Stay for dinner.

191
00:09:51,430 --> 00:09:52,270
- Yes.
- I'll make some food.

192
00:09:52,470 --> 00:09:54,120
No, it's too much trouble. I'm leaving.

193
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,880
Not at all. It'll be ready in a minute.

194
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,360
- No, thanks.
- Yes, Jiali.

195
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,880
Eat the eggs.

196
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:00,470
I'll bring you more when you're done.

197
00:10:00,710 --> 00:10:02,550
I've got

198
00:10:02,550 --> 00:10:03,710
the chicken feed for Mom.

199
00:10:03,780 --> 00:10:05,120
(Compound Chicken Feed)
I'll send it to her.

200
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:05,880
I'll take it home.

201
00:10:05,880 --> 00:10:07,280
No, it's too heavy for you.

202
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:08,520
Ok, then.

203
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,580
- I'm leaving.
- Then...

204
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:11,950
No.

205
00:10:11,950 --> 00:10:12,790
Aunt, bye.

206
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:13,620
Bye, Guangming.

207
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:14,610
Take care, Jiali.

208
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:31,950
Son, play by yourself for a bit.

209
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,040
Liu Xiaoling, are you a dog?

210
00:10:42,470 --> 00:10:44,640
Why are you nervous if you did nothing wrong?

211
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:47,640
What's wrong with you?

212
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:48,830
Stop sniffing. Stop.

213
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:51,470
This is not the first time, Tang Zhenmin.

214
00:10:51,470 --> 00:10:52,590
It's the same cloying,

215
00:10:52,590 --> 00:10:54,190
stinky woman's perfume from last time.

216
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,000
Smell it yourself.

217
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,190
Isn't this the smell of sweat?

218
00:11:01,470 --> 00:11:02,830
You didn't wash it clean.

219
00:11:02,830 --> 00:11:04,240
If you tell me the truth,

220
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,400
I'll let it go.

221
00:11:05,590 --> 00:11:07,190
But if you lie to me and I find out,

222
00:11:07,190 --> 00:11:08,280
I'm not done with you.

223
00:11:11,590 --> 00:11:13,190
I admit I danced,

224
00:11:13,780 --> 00:11:15,000
but I only danced a little.

225
00:11:15,590 --> 00:11:17,190
Didn't you promise me

226
00:11:17,190 --> 00:11:18,880
you'd never dance behind my back again?

227
00:11:20,430 --> 00:11:21,790
With that Wang Aiju again?

228
00:11:27,830 --> 00:11:28,670
Fine.

229
00:11:29,550 --> 00:11:31,160
You live with her. I'll go.

230
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:32,880
Liu Xiaoling,

231
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:34,950
if you run away from home again,

232
00:11:34,950 --> 00:11:36,160
don't expect me to pick you up.

233
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:42,190
This is my home.

234
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,280
If anyone's leaving, it's you!

235
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:45,190
Fine, this is your home. I'll go!

236
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:55,070
Ma'am, the tea is ready.

237
00:11:56,470 --> 00:11:57,880
Try this, first flush of the year.

238
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:01,360
You'd better calm down.

239
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:04,880
Why don't you stay at Mom's for a while?

240
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:07,070
I'm not going.

241
00:12:07,190 --> 00:12:08,400
She'll scold me again.

242
00:12:08,430 --> 00:12:10,040
She always takes his side.

243
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:11,190
Why don't you

244
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:13,000
go to see Qiufang?

245
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:14,960
Definitely not.

246
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:17,070
Since she married into the Tang family,

247
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:18,670
she's thought of herself as a family member.

248
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:19,830
She only helps them.

249
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:22,950
Maybe it's not as bad as you think.

250
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:25,640
I don't think Zhenmin is that kind of guy.

251
00:12:26,530 --> 00:12:27,370
Jiayi,

252
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,190
what I hate the most

253
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:31,430
is that he's idle all day long.

254
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:33,000
He doesn't make much money.

255
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,000
It's killing me.

256
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:37,190
Didn't I tell you to let him

257
00:12:37,190 --> 00:12:38,400
quit his job and start a business?

258
00:12:38,550 --> 00:12:39,760
Do you think he will listen?

259
00:12:39,830 --> 00:12:41,280
He doesn't take any advice.

260
00:12:41,710 --> 00:12:42,670
Many people around us

261
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:44,400
have made their fortunes in business,

262
00:12:44,430 --> 00:12:46,040
like his eldest brother

263
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:47,710
and your husband.

264
00:12:48,070 --> 00:12:49,520
The government encourages

265
00:12:49,520 --> 00:12:51,520
some people to get rich first.

266
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:52,790
If you don't move forward,

267
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:54,190
how can you get rich first?

268
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:55,470
So some people don't lose

269
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:57,240
because of their ability,

270
00:12:57,400 --> 00:13:00,590
but because of their attitude and vision.

271
00:13:00,880 --> 00:13:02,590
You're absolutely right, Jiayi.

272
00:13:04,590 --> 00:13:05,790
Why don't I quit my job?

273
00:13:05,950 --> 00:13:07,030
You quit?

274
00:13:07,550 --> 00:13:08,430
You can't.

275
00:13:08,790 --> 00:13:09,630
Why?

276
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:12,070
You got Dad's job.

277
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:13,790
If you quit,

278
00:13:13,830 --> 00:13:15,590
Ouyang wouldn't dare help you.

279
00:13:15,590 --> 00:13:17,670
Dad's job is just a job.

280
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:19,160
It's not a title.

281
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:21,590
It's a secure job.

282
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:24,400
It has become insecure long ago.

283
00:13:25,570 --> 00:13:27,000
Still, it's different.

284
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:28,240
You have a family

285
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,400
