00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:39,030
Changsheng,

574
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:41,750
come and get the money.

575
00:29:43,320 --> 00:29:46,360
Mom said she couldn't come up the mountain

576
00:29:46,360 --> 00:29:47,360
because of her leg.

577
00:29:47,360 --> 00:29:49,400
She asked us to burn paper money for you.

578
00:29:49,600 --> 00:29:52,560
Bless everyone of our family

579
00:29:53,190 --> 00:29:55,560
in heaven.

580
00:30:04,470 --> 00:30:06,320
Come on. Take the money.

581
00:30:11,900 --> 00:30:15,920
♪Let's say we're close to each other♪

582
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:20,830
♪We're each other's beloved♪

583
00:30:22,100 --> 00:30:26,720
♪Whose fate and youth♪

584
00:30:27,390 --> 00:30:31,060
♪As if a lifetime had passed♪

585
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:36,230
♪Let's say we love each other♪

586
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:41,280
♪We'll never leave each other♪

587
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:46,840
♪Believe in love after all the storms♪

588
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:51,440
♪I believe in everything you say♪

589
00:30:52,800 --> 00:30:53,840
It's beautiful.

590
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:56,030
As always.

591
00:30:56,030 --> 00:30:56,870
Yes.

592
00:30:57,060 --> 00:31:01,700
♪May time stop when we first met♪

593
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:06,670
Jiali, so,

594
00:31:07,670 --> 00:31:09,080
shall we call it a day

595
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:10,080
and go home?

596
00:31:10,810 --> 00:31:11,760
Jiahuan is busy.

597
00:31:11,760 --> 00:31:12,640
Xiaoling isn't here, either.

598
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:14,880
Not everyone's here. Let's just skip it.

599
00:31:15,470 --> 00:31:16,310
Ok.

600
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:19,880
How did it go with your job?

601
00:31:20,600 --> 00:31:22,430
Weiguo's sister is trying to

602
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:24,510
get me into the pharmaceutical plant.

603
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:25,720
Ok.

604
00:31:26,030 --> 00:31:27,190
People can't avoid

605
00:31:27,190 --> 00:31:28,160
getting sick,

606
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:29,320
and when they do, they need medicine.

607
00:31:29,530 --> 00:31:31,920
It's just a collective enterprise,

608
00:31:32,080 --> 00:31:33,510
not a secure job.

609
00:31:35,230 --> 00:31:36,120
These days,

610
00:31:36,990 --> 00:31:38,990
except for civil servants,

611
00:31:39,470 --> 00:31:40,800
financial institutions

612
00:31:40,950 --> 00:31:41,880
like Jiahuan's workplace,

613
00:31:42,470 --> 00:31:44,990
coal mines, and power plants,

614
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:47,890
there's no such thing as a secure job.

615
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:52,120
Yes. I kind of envy Jiayi.

616
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:55,400
She had gone through hard work for years

617
00:31:55,560 --> 00:31:57,510
before she succeeded accidentally.

618
00:31:57,970 --> 00:31:59,320
Don't envy her.

619
00:32:00,320 --> 00:32:02,110
Not everyone can do business.

620
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:05,580
Yeah. Anyway, we have to

621
00:32:05,900 --> 00:32:07,060
make our own living

622
00:32:07,220 --> 00:32:08,220
and show our own prowess.

623
00:32:10,740 --> 00:32:11,580
Jiali.

624
00:32:17,740 --> 00:32:18,580
Come on.

625
00:32:27,780 --> 00:32:28,660
It's so nice.

626
00:32:49,260 --> 00:32:50,980
(Make contributions to the country)

627
00:32:50,980 --> 00:32:52,740
(New recruits enlisted with honor)

628
00:32:52,740 --> 00:32:57,740
(Mutual support between the people and army)

629
00:33:02,460 --> 00:33:03,980
Behave when you get there.

630
00:33:04,590 --> 00:33:05,860
Don't make trouble.

631
00:33:06,180 --> 00:33:07,020
Yes.

632
00:33:07,180 --> 00:33:08,140
He won't.

633
00:33:08,220 --> 00:33:09,380
He won't.

634
00:33:09,580 --> 00:33:10,420
Xiaonian,

635
00:33:10,580 --> 00:33:13,340
behave when you are in the army.

636
00:33:13,340 --> 00:33:14,180
Yes.

637
00:33:14,250 --> 00:33:15,180
Don't make trouble.

638
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:17,220
Xiaonian, take this.

639
00:33:17,700 --> 00:33:18,740
No, no.

640
00:33:18,740 --> 00:33:19,580
Mom, no need.

641
00:33:19,580 --> 00:33:20,740
He'll get an allowance there.

642
00:33:20,740 --> 00:33:21,620
Take it.

643
00:33:21,620 --> 00:33:23,180
It won't cost him anything there.

644
00:33:24,860 --> 00:33:25,940
Thank Grandma.

645
00:33:25,940 --> 00:33:26,820
Thank you, Grandma.

646
00:33:26,820 --> 00:33:27,820
Don't spend it recklessly.

647
00:33:28,490 --> 00:33:29,330
I know.

648
00:33:33,860 --> 00:33:35,180
Write to us.

649
00:33:35,660 --> 00:33:36,980
Don't worry.

650
00:33:37,060 --> 00:33:38,380
He's stationed in the province.

651
00:33:38,740 --> 00:33:39,990
- Just try not to make trouble.
- It's close.

652
00:33:41,780 --> 00:33:42,780
I'm so happy.

653
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:45,970
All assemble!

654
00:33:49,700 --> 00:33:50,540
Go ahead.

655
00:33:50,820 --> 00:33:52,220
I'll wait a little longer.

656
00:33:52,380 --> 00:33:53,220
Who are you waiting for?

657
00:33:53,900 --> 00:33:55,290
Xiaofang said she would see me off.

658
00:33:55,570 --> 00:33:56,580
Which Xiaofang?

659
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:57,740
Tang Xiaofang.

660
00:33:57,880 --> 00:33:58,860
You'll be late.

661
00:33:59,070 --> 00:34:01,390
He Xiangdong, attention, turn around!

662
00:34:01,990 --> 00:34:02,900
Hurry up.

663
00:34:03,960 --> 00:34:04,800
Get in line!

664
00:34:11,940 --> 00:34:12,820
They radiate energy.

665
00:34:14,660 --> 00:34:15,500
It's

666
00:34:16,140 --> 00:34:17,620
like a dream.

667
00:34:18,140 --> 00:34:19,340
This is the same truck I rode in

668
00:34:19,340 --> 00:34:20,700
when I went to the countryside.

669
00:34:25,380 --> 00:34:26,220
It's ok.

670
00:34:26,540 --> 00:34:28,380
He's never left home yet.

671
00:34:29,180 --> 00:34:30,020
Don't worry.

672
00:34:30,060 --> 00:34:30,900
Everyone,

673
00:34:30,980 --> 00:34:31,820
attention!

674
00:34:32,740 --> 00:34:34,020
Right face!

675
00:34:35,940 --> 00:34:37,060
Face forward!

676
00:34:37,490 --> 00:34:38,330
At ease!

677
00:34:38,660 --> 00:34:39,500
Attention!

678
00:34:43,100 --> 00:34:46,260
(Honor)

679
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:51,530
I should have claimed your tile just now,

680
00:34:51,540 --> 00:34:52,660
then I would win.

681
00:34:52,860 --> 00:34:54,340
You've got a good hand of tiles.

682
00:34:54,360 --> 00:34:55,240
Yes.

683
00:34:55,260 --> 00:34:56,820
What a good hand.

684
00:34:56,820 --> 00:34:58,140
Jianguo, you're back.

685
00:35:04,620 --> 00:35:06,340
Let's finish this game and call it a day.

686
00:35:06,340 --> 00:35:08,220
No, I haven't made my money back.

687
00:35:09,140 --> 00:35:10,300
Then we'll play with you for a while.

688
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:11,540
Two more games.

689
00:35:19,660 --> 00:35:20,540
It's ok.

690
00:35:21,180 --> 00:35:22,060
Come on.

691
00:35:34,020 --> 00:35:34,860
One less.

692
00:35:35,060 --> 00:35:36,740
Ok, that's enough for today.

693
00:35:36,740 --> 00:35:37,780
We'll play again some other time.

694
00:35:38,100 --> 00:35:38,940
It's ok.

695
00:35:39,140 --> 00:35:40,100
We have plenty of time.

696
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:42,660
I'm sure you'll get your money back.

697
00:35:43,460 --> 00:35:44,940
Jianguo, we're leaving.

698
00:35:45,660 --> 00:35:46,500
Some other time.

699
00:35:48,620 --> 00:35:49,660
Jiali, let's play some other time.

700
00:36:04,740 --> 00:36:05,580
What's wrong?

701
00:36:06,220 --> 00:36:07,340
Do you have a problem with me?

702
00:36:07,900 --> 00:36:08,740
No.

703
00:36:09,620 --> 00:36:11,060
Yes, you do.

704
00:36:12,260 --> 00:36:13,660
It was just for fun.

705
00:36:14,260 --> 00:36:15,660
What's with the long face?

706
00:36:16,060 --> 00:36:17,300
Was it just for fun?

707
00:36:18,420 --> 00:36:19,460
You were gambling.

708
00:36:21,140 --> 00:36:22,340
Only ten cents a game.

709
00:36:22,860 --> 00:36:24,460
I was just passing the time.

710
00:36:25,060 --> 00:36:26,660
Why are you making a big deal out of this?

711
00:36:30,140 --> 00:36:30,980
Jiali,

712
00:36:32,220 --> 00:36:33,460
I understand you're in a bad mood

713
00:36:33,460 --> 00:36:34,340
after you were laid off.

714
00:36:34,700 --> 00:36:36,060
And our son is in the army.

715
00:36:36,940 --> 00:36:39,620
You have a hard time getting over it.

716
00:36:39,820 --> 00:36:41,060
That's why I gave you time.

717
00:36:42,100 --> 00:36:43,860
But you can't do this always.

718
00:36:43,860 --> 00:36:45,140
You play mahjong every day.

719
00:36:45,140 --> 00:36:46,700
You're almost fixed on the table.

720
00:36:46,820 --> 00:36:48,460
If I don't play, what can I do?

721
00:36:48,540 --> 00:36:49,420
Anything

722
00:36:49,420 --> 00:36:50,620
is better than playing mahjong.

723
00:36:50,660 --> 00:36:52,740
I've worked with vegetables half my life.

724
00:36:52,860 --> 00:36:53,900
I don't know what else to do.

725
00:36:55,740 --> 00:36:57,660
You can still work with vegetables.

726
00:36:58,540 --> 00:36:59,900
People have to work.

727
00:37:00,060 --> 00:37:02,140
Staying idle at home every day,

728
00:37:02,670 --> 00:37:03,860
forget making money,

729
00:37:04,260 --> 00:37:06,100
you will fall apart mentally.

730
00:37:10,540 --> 00:37:12,550
My world has fallen apart long ago.

731
00:37:22,460 --> 00:37:23,300
Jiali,

732
00:37:24,460 --> 00:37:25,940
as long as you pull yourself together,

733
00:37:26,540 --> 00:37:28,260
whatever you do, I'll support you.

734
00:37:28,340 --> 00:37:29,660
You can make it.

735
00:37:32,700 --> 00:37:33,900
Now that you've been laid off,

736
00:37:35,060 --> 00:37:36,300
change your track.

737
00:37:36,860 --> 00:37:38,260
You'll still have a great life.

738
00:37:38,540 --> 00:37:39,900
You have a secure life.

739
00:37:39,900 --> 00:37:41,140
You don't understand.

740
00:37:42,260 --> 00:37:43,460
Even if I don't,

741
00:37:44,340 --> 00:37:45,740
could it be harder than the past,

742
00:37:46,030 --> 00:37:47,760
than when we got married?

743
00:37:48,540 --> 00:37:49,740
It's much harder!

744
00:37:57,740 --> 00:37:58,940
It was hard then.

745
00:37:59,660 --> 00:38:01,260
But we were still young at that time.

746
00:38:01,300 --> 00:38:02,780
You're not old now.

747
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:06,260
You're lying to yourself and me.

748
00:38:06,260 --> 00:38:07,780
I'm not a child.

749
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:09,540
Jiali,

750
00:38:09,900 --> 00:38:11,260
once you start to work,

751
00:38:12,260 --> 00:38:13,700
everything will be different.

752
00:38:13,740 --> 00:38:14,780
How do I start?

753
00:38:14,860 --> 00:38:15,980
I only know how to sell vegetables.

754
00:38:16,260 --> 00:38:17,140
No problem.

755
00:38:18,060 --> 00:38:20,180
That's it. I'll support you.

756
00:38:23,660 --> 00:38:25,060
You're a cadre.

757
00:38:25,340 --> 00:38:27,180
If your wife runs a stall in the market,

758
00:38:27,460 --> 00:38:28,660
wouldn't it make you ashamed?

759
00:38:28,900 --> 00:38:30,540
There's nothing to be ashamed of.

760
00:38:31,500 --> 00:38:33,660
Even if you're not ashamed, I am.

761
00:38:33,660 --> 00:38:34,980
My life is getting worse.

762
00:38:35,460 --> 00:38:37,580
You're not thinking straight.

763
00:38:38,100 --> 00:38:39,420
Don't you think you've regressed

764
00:38:39,420 --> 00:38:40,700
in your consciousness?

765
00:38:41,180 --> 00:38:43,300
All honest labor holds equal dignity.

766
00:38:43,740 --> 00:38:45,100
Every legitimate job well done

767
00:38:45,100 --> 00:38:46,260
writes its own medal of honor.

768
00:38:46,580 --> 00:38:48,580
This isn't the old days.

769
00:38:49,310 --> 00:38:51,580
It was honorable to be a waste collector.

770
00:38:51,660 --> 00:38:52,980
I did it before.

771
00:38:53,380 --> 00:38:54,980
Whoever earns money is honorable now.

772
00:38:57,700 --> 00:38:59,540
As long as you can demonstrate your value,

773
00:38:59,540 --> 00:39:00,380
you are honorable.

774
00:39:05,340 --> 00:39:07,100
We don't have any start-up money.

775
00:39:07,100 --> 00:39:08,540
We spent all our savings

776
00:39:09,140 --> 00:39:10,860
to buy out this house.

777
00:39:13,900 --> 00:39:14,740
Then we'll borrow.

778
00:39:17,060 --> 00:39:18,500
I'll ask my colleagues.

779
00:39:21,300 --> 00:39:22,300
I'll figure it out.

780
00:39:25,900 --> 00:39:26,900
Sir, Ma'am,

781
00:39:27,100 --> 00:39:28,100
your sister is here.

782
00:39:28,500 --> 00:39:29,340
Got it.

783
00:39:29,900 --> 00:39:30,740
Coming.

784
00:39:32,960 --> 00:39:33,800
Ms. Liao,

785
00:39:33,900 --> 00:39:35,700
make my sister some Biluochun Tea.

786
00:39:35,700 --> 00:39:36,540
- Ouyang.
- Yes.

787
00:39:36,660 --> 00:39:37,500
Jiali.

788
00:39:37,580 --> 00:39:38,860
Did I interrupt your rest?

789
00:39:38,900 --> 00:39:39,740
It's ok.

790
00:39:39,980 --> 00:39:40,820
Jiali,

791
00:39:41,500 --> 00:39:42,460
what's up?

792
00:39:43,460 --> 00:39:45,460
I have a favor to ask of you.

793
00:39:46,740 --> 00:39:47,580
Take a seat.

794
00:39:47,770 --> 00:39:48,610
Sit down first.

795
00:39:50,020 --> 00:39:51,180
What is it, Jiali?

796
00:39:52,740 --> 00:39:53,580
No, thanks.

797
00:39:54,630 --> 00:39:57,300
It's been a while since I was laid off.

798
00:39:57,300 --> 00:39:59,660
I can't stay idle forever.

799
00:40:00,100 --> 00:40:02,780
I'm thinking of starting a small business.

800
00:40:03,340 --> 00:40:04,700
What kind of business?

801
00:40:05,980 --> 00:40:07,060
I haven't made up my mind.

802
00:40:08,060 --> 00:40:09,100
The same old business, probably.

803
00:40:09,900 --> 00:40:11,860
Why don't you work for Ouyang?

804
00:40:12,420 --> 00:40:13,540
He's got a job opening.

805
00:40:14,820 --> 00:40:16,540
If you want to join us, no problem.

806
00:40:17,900 --> 00:40:19,100
He's business is big.

807
00:40:19,100 --> 00:40:19,980
I don't know how to do it.

808
00:40:19,980 --> 00:40:20,940
I'm flattered.

809
00:40:21,380 --> 00:40:23,180
Besides, he has many brothers

810
00:40:23,180 --> 00:40:24,260
who can help him.

811
00:40:24,260 --> 00:40:25,540
He doesn't need a woman like me.

812
00:40:25,900 --> 00:40:27,060
I don't want to cause trouble.

813
00:40:27,060 --> 00:40:27,900
It's ok, Jiali.

814
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:29,060
If you want to join us,

815
00:40:29,060 --> 00:40:30,700
I'll give you an easy job.

816
00:40:30,700 --> 00:40:31,540
No, no.

817
00:40:31,660 --> 00:40:32,500
I don't think so.

818
00:40:32,980 --> 00:40:34,300
It's not good that I depend on you

819
00:40:34,300 --> 00:40:36,100
for a living.

820
00:40:36,660 --> 00:40:37,660
What do you think, then?

821
00:40:39,300 --> 00:40:43,100
My savings are due at the end of this month.

822
00:40:43,900 --> 00:40:46,780
I want to borrow some from you first.

823
00:40:46,780 --> 00:40:47,980
I'll pay you back at the end of the month.

824
00:40:47,980 --> 00:40:48,820
How much do you need?

825
00:40:50,900 --> 00:40:51,740
3,000.

826
00:40:55,060 --> 00:40:55,900
I'll get it.

827
00:40:59,500 --> 00:41:00,580
Thanks, Jiayi.

828
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:04,300
Have some tea, please.

829
00:41:08,500 --> 00:41:10,060
Jiali, count it.

830
00:41:10,340 --> 00:41:12,140
No need. You do a big business.

831
00:41:12,140 --> 00:41:13,860
You're more careful with it than we do.

832
00:41:19,180 --> 00:41:20,020
Ms. Liao,

833
00:41:20,660 --> 00:41:21,940
get me a pen and paper.

834
00:41:23,140 --> 00:41:25,140
Why do you need it?

835
00:41:26,260 --> 00:41:27,100
Ma'am.

836
00:41:30,660 --> 00:41:31,500
Here, Jiali.

837
00:41:31,700 --> 00:41:32,700
Write me an IOU.

838
00:41:34,510 --> 00:41:35,350
Jiali,

839
00:41:35,540 --> 00:41:36,900
you don't have to.

840
00:41:37,090 --> 00:41:38,980
We don't need an IOU.

841
00:41:40,640 --> 00:41:41,480
I'll write one.

842
00:41:41,700 --> 00:41:43,260
- No.
- I'm glad Jiayi reminded me.

843
00:41:43,260 --> 00:41:44,580
Yes, it's good to write one.

844
00:41:44,780 --> 00:41:46,500
We'll make it clear.

845
00:41:53,020 --> 00:41:54,380
Why do you have to do this?

846
00:42:13,960 --> 00:42:15,300
- Tear it up.
- No.

847
00:42:16,900 --> 00:42:18,540
Even brothers keep clear accounts.

848
00:42:19,060 --> 00:42:21,060
You lent me money out of goodwill.

849
00:42:21,060 --> 00:42:23,260
I wrote this as a matter of responsibility.

850
00:42:23,580 --> 00:42:25,100
It's the right thing to do on both counts.

851
00:42:27,700 --> 00:42:28,860
We don't have to be so formal.

852
00:42:29,740 --> 00:42:30,900
Ok, I'm leaving.

853
00:42:30,900 --> 00:42:31,900
I won't bother you anymore.

854
00:42:36,060 --> 00:42:36,900
Bye, Ouyang.

855
00:42:38,740 --> 00:42:40,380
Jiali, I'm not walking you out.

856
00:42:45,540 --> 00:42:46,420
What's wrong with you?

857
00:42:47,260 --> 00:42:48,580
